steps.html_instructions: Head north on R. do Hospício toward R. Princesa Isabel
Turn left at the 1st cross street onto R. Gervásio Pires
Turn right onto R. Barão de São Borja
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto R. Gen. Joaquim Inácio
Continue onto Av. Sport Clube do Recife

Continue onto Av. Eng. Abdias de Carvalho
Pass by KiYoi Galetos (Abdias de Carvalho) (on the right in 3.1 km)

Keep left to continue on Av. Eng. Abdias de Carvalho/Viaduto Alça do Viaduto Ceasa
Continue to follow Viaduto Alça do Viaduto Ceasa
Keep right to stay on Av. Senador Helvídio Nunes
Keep right to stay on Av. Senador Helvídio Nunes
At the roundabout, continue straight onto BR-230/BR-316
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit and stay on BR-230/BR-316

Keep left to continue on Rod. Cap. Pedro Teixeira/BR-316/BR-343
Continue to follow Rod. Cap. Pedro Teixeira
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto BR-226/BR-316 heading to Belém
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit and stay on BR-226/BR-316

Slight right to stay on BR-316
Pass by Novo Lar Construções (on the right in 3.8 km)
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit and stay on BR-316
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto R. Alto da Cruz
R. Alto da Cruz turns slightly right and becomes R. Aarão Réis
